package - pip3 install django

1. create Project
    -  django-admin startproject school_management (project_name)
    -  cd school_management

2. Database connection and update
    - python3 manage.py makemigrations
    - python3 manage.py migrate

3. Execute project - python3 manage.py runserver
4. Stop project - control + c

5. create super user
    -  python3 manage.py createsuperuser

6. Create New App
    - python3 manage.py startapp student (app_name)
    - added App Name in project_folder/settings.py --> INSTALLED_APPS

    - Create a Model in app_folder/models.py
    - Update database with new Model
        - python3 manage.py makemigrations
        - python3 manage.py migrate

    - Add model to admin.py file
    - Run Server


